  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb8b",
      "text": "(Column) SMART criteria",
      "created": 1547363363,
      "updated": 1553662866,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb8c",
      "text": "Related to [(1.2.2.1) Clarify the goal], [SMART criteria] give us a useful viewpoint to the quality of goal settings. It appears in 1981.",
      "created": 1547364474,
      "updated": 1553660089,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb8d",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1547364487,
      "updated": 1547364487,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb8e",
      "text": "It is called SMART, taking the initials os Specific, Measurable, Assignable, Realistic, Time-related. I explain these 5 items briefly as follows.",
      "created": 1547364475,
      "updated": 1547364490,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb8f",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1547364475,
      "updated": 1547364475,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb90",
      "text": " [* Specific]: Specific areas to be improved are clear",
      "created": 1547364491,
      "updated": 1547364503,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb91",
      "text": " [* Measurable]: There is an amount, or at least an indicator showing progress",
      "created": 1547364500,
      "updated": 1547364520,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb92",
      "text": " [* Assignable]: It is clear who is going to execute the plan",
      "created": 1547364500,
      "updated": 1547364500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb93",
      "text": " [* Realistic]: Realistically achievable, given resources necessary for the implementation",
      "created": 1547364500,
      "updated": 1547364500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb94",
      "text": " [* Time-related]: When is the result obtained",
      "created": 1547364500,
      "updated": 1547364500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb95",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1547364500,
      "updated": 1547364500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb96",
      "text": "This criterion is for organizational goal setting. When you use it for your individual goal setting, it is somewhat over spec. To think you must fit these standards, setting a goal itself becomes a psychological burden. I recommend using the standards to help to understand which goals are bad.",
      "created": 1547364522,
      "updated": 1547364598,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb97",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1547364598,
      "updated": 1547364598,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb98",
      "text": "Note",
      "created": 1547364599,
      "updated": 1547364612,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb99",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553593939,
      "updated": 1553593939,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb9a",
      "text": "\t*1 Oran, G. T. (1981). \"There's a S.M.A.R.T. write management's goals and objectives\".  Management  Review,  70  (11),  35-36.",
      "created": 1547364612,
      "updated": 1547364626,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb9b",
      "text": " *2 Sometimes A corresponds Achievable (realistically achievable, given necessary resources) and R corresponds Responsible (it is clear who is responsible for executing the plan). Although A and R exchanged each other,  the concept of five factors are almost the same.",
      "created": 1547364614,
      "updated": 1547364639,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb9c",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1547364612,
      "updated": 1547364612,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb9d",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1553593951,
      "updated": 1553593951,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb9e",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553593951,
      "updated": 1553593951,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fb9f",
      "text": "Keywords:",
      "created": 1553593945,
      "updated": 1553593949,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba0",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553593949,
      "updated": 1553593949,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba1",
      "text": "\t[Specific]",
      "created": 1547364644,
      "updated": 1547364649,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba2",
      "text": "\t[Measurable]",
      "created": 1547364645,
      "updated": 1547364678,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba3",
      "text": "\t[Assignable] / [Achievable]",
      "created": 1547364661,
      "updated": 1547364687,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba4",
      "text": "\t[Realistic] / [Responsible]",
      "created": 1547364668,
      "updated": 1547364698,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba5",
      "text": "\t[Time-related]",
      "created": 1547364672,
      "updated": 1547364675,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba6",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1547364657,
      "updated": 1547364657,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba7",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1553593953,
      "updated": 1553593954,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba8",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553593956,
      "updated": 1553593956,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fba9",
      "text": "Raleted:",
      "created": 1547364699,
      "updated": 1547364702,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fbaa",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553593955,
      "updated": 1553593955,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fbab",
      "text": "\tSpecific: [concrete]",
      "created": 1547364702,
      "updated": 1547364711,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fbac",
      "text": "\tAchievable: [unknown achievement condition]",
      "created": 1547364713,
      "updated": 1547364738,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fbad",
      "text": "\tMeasurable: [(2.3.2.5) Measure, dismiss, put together], [(4.3.2.3) Measure and control speed].",
      "created": 1547364701,
      "updated": 1553661587,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fbae",
      "text": "\tTime-related: [cutting by time], [Make the goal closer]",
      "created": 1547364766,
      "updated": 1553594049,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
